text: Yrjö Lampila (23 April 1901 - 18 October 1963) was a Finnish diver. He competed in the men's 10 metre platform event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1901 births Category:1963 deaths Category:Finnish male divers Category:Olympic divers of Finland Category:Divers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Helsinki
